    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sifra is a fast-paced roguelike first-person shooter with a strong focus on build-crafting and synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/0bc6f5aed1f1fd1cd6c09bd6f239ca7e.poster.avif?t=1736454154\" width=800 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/0bc6f5aed1f1fd1cd6c09bd6f239ca7e.webm?t=1736454154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/0bc6f5aed1f1fd1cd6c09bd6f239ca7e.mp4?t=1736454154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each upgrade during the run is highly impactful and changes your playstyle. The upgrades are designed to allow you to be creative and sometimes break the game in unexpected ways - even for the devs themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you beat the game is not a matter of grind but how you learn the systems and get better in the builds and executing them. Meta progression doesn’t make your character stronger, but instead gives you more options to play with.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/845102dfd6a9ff7ac188c0989e20b576.poster.avif?t=1736454154\" width=800 height=486 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/845102dfd6a9ff7ac188c0989e20b576.webm?t=1736454154\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145600/extras/845102dfd6a9ff7ac188c0989e20b576.mp4?t=1736454154\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wishlist now!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the links section to join our discord server</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
